>d</span></span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">]</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">0.8750</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.036em;">ν</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.085em;">N</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">+</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">0.3137</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.036em;">ν</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">+</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1.0</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">+</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">0.6275</span></span> <span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">/</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.085em;">N</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> </p><figure class="image image_resized" style="width:74.96%"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/v8kegffip7w1si8iitps" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/vsqaskbhbkl66tssvzgs 210w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/bhjsjznanndaw65p1swm 420w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/bugxsdysrzhehpecyqt5 630w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/wzyoxlewxarlk9uyxmps 840w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/lnr93ksrclvqygwcjkhr 1050w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/sylukz6wxe4upclgwkpi 1260w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/lk3yjwknkhbvmrxatk3l 1470w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/wgxqgudzrlugg01tl9vm 1680w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/yk4dwjz5kkefofkpbehy 1890w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/p4pfudyeojrhgdliyods 2060w"><figcaption>如果您选择红色或蓝色，则预期效用作为玩家数量的函数。使选择蓝色变得明智所需的玩家数量取决于你的利他主义<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\nu"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.036em;">ν</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ，即你对相对于自己的陌生人的重视程度。</figcaption></figure><p>这里的常数项是你自己生存的概率（以及预期效用）。</p><p>第二项与你对他人生命相对于你自己的生命的价值<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\nu"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.036em;">ν</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>成正比，来自于你可能进行决胜一票的可能性：这里<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="N"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.085em;">N</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>被抵消，因为随着概率的降低，你可以拯救的人数会增加，因此选择蓝色因果关系平均可以节省大约 1/3 的人的时间 (0.6275-0.3137)。 （最后一项也与决胜局有关，但随着<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="N"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.085em;">N</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>变大，它会消失，无论如何，这两种情况都是相同的。）</p><p>第一项与<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="N"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.085em;">N</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>成正比，代表通过因果关系使他人受益的潜力，显然如果您选择蓝色，则效果会更大。只要<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\nu > 0"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.036em;">ν</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">>;</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">0</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ，随着玩家数量的增加，该项最终将压倒其他因素，这意味着任何关心（线性）其他人的人都应该选择蓝色作为较大的<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="N"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.085em;">N</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>值。</p><p><strong>综上所述：</strong></p><p><strong>如果玩家数量至少是你愿意拯救的最小人数的 2-3 倍，你会想要选择蓝色。</strong></p><ul><li>对于 ν=0.1：如果 N >; 22.01，则选择蓝色</li><li>对于 ν=0.01：如果 N >; 261.44，则选择蓝色</li><li>对于 ν=0.001：如果 N >; 2655.73，则选择蓝色</li></ul><p>我发现这个结果非常违反直觉。这也让我很混蛋，因为我最初选择了红色。但让我试着稍微变蓝一点。我认为这个论点是这样的：红色可以帮助你个人生存。但在一个偏向蓝色的社会中，平均而言，有更多的人能够生存下来。如果有足够多的人面临生命危险，那么让社会变得更蓝一点将比你自己的生命风险更重要。</p><p>说实话，我不知道我是否有勇气根据令人毛骨悚然的相关性来选择 18% 的死亡几率。 </p><p></p><ol class="footnotes" role="doc-endnotes"><li class="footnote-item" role="doc-endnote" id="fns4iy3ko6k4e"> <span class="footnote-back-link"><sup><strong><a href="#fnrefs4iy3ko6k4e">^</a></strong></sup></span><div class="footnote-content"><p>如果你的效用是幸存者数量的对数怎么办？我认为这不会有太大区别，因为那样你还必须考虑到世界上每个玩得不好的人。如果<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="N"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.085em;">N</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>小于十亿左右，你对这<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="N"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.085em;">N</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>个人的边际效用仍然大致呈线性。如果您在<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="N=1"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.085em;">N</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">10</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>亿的线性边际效用下选择蓝色，那么增加<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="N"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.085em;">N</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>应该不会改变您的想法。如果您在<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="N="><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.085em;">N</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 10 亿时选择红色，那是因为您的利他主义值<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\nu"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.036em;">ν</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>非常接近于零，并且无论如何您都可能会选择红色。</p></div></li></ol><br/><br/> <a href="https://www.lesswrong.com/posts/ogcEgWEgmzBw8ePMC/red-pill-vs-blue-pill-bayes-style#comments">讨论</a>; https://www.lesswrong.com/posts/